What is Furniture E-Commerce?
Furniture e-commerce refers to the online sale of furniture items, including sofas, beds, tables, and chairs, among others. This market encompasses various product types, such as solid wood furniture, board type furniture, soft furniture, and others, catering to both residential and commercial applications. In North America, high internet penetration and advanced digital platforms enable consumers to easily compare prices, styles, and reviews-fundamentally transforming how households and businesses furnish their spaces.
